            <div type="edition" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                <note>The text is taken from <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/V63EFJAW"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Budge1915Mercurius"/><title level="m">Miscellaneous Coptic texts in the dialect of Upper Egypt</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">E. A. Wallis</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Budge</t:surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>Printed by order of the Trustees : sold at the British Museum</publisher><date>1915</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/miscellaneouscop00budguoft/page/n9/mode/2up</note><citedRange unit="page">1161</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                <ab>ዝንቱ፡ ነገር፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ወብፁዕ፡ ሰማዕት፡ መርቆርዮስ። በመዋዕለ፡ ዴኬዎስ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ሮሜ፡ ተወልደ፡ ሕፃን፡ ፒሉፓዲር፡
                    ዘበትርጓሜሁ፡ መርቆሬዎስ። ወስመ፡ አቡሁ፡ አሮስ፡ ወስመ፡ እምሔዉ፡ ሲዳሮስ፡ ወ፪ኤሆሙ፡ ነዓውያነ፡ አራዋት። ወእምከመ፡ አኀዙ፡
                    ይወስዱ፡ ለነገሥት፡ ወለመኳንንት፡ ወለመላእክት፡ ወይሁብዎሙ፡ ዓሥቦሙ ። ወመጽኡ፡ ፪ገጸ፡  ከልብ፡ እምርኁቅ፡ ብሔር፡ ወበጽሑ፡
                    ኀበ፡ መሥገርት፡ ወኀሡም፡ ርእየቶሙ፡ ወሥዕርተ፡ ርእሶሙ፡ ከመ፡ ሥዕርተ፡ ፈረስ፡ ወስነኒሆሙ፡ ከመ፡ ስነነ፡ አናብስት፡
                    ወአዕይንቲሆሙ፡ ከመ፡ እሳት፡ እደዊሆሙ፡ ወእገሪሆሙ፡ ከመ፡ በትረ፡ ሐፂን፡ </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="edition" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                <note>The text is taken from <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/V63EFJAW"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Budge1915Mercurius"/><title level="m">Miscellaneous Coptic texts in the dialect of Upper Egypt</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">E. A. Wallis</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Budge</t:surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>Printed by order of the Trustees : sold at the British Museum</publisher><date>1915</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/miscellaneouscop00budguoft/page/n9/mode/2up</note><citedRange unit="page">1187</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                <ab>ወሶበ፡ ርእዩ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶሳት፡ ተፈሥሑ፡ ወባረክዎ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር። አመ፡ የሐውር፡ ውስተ፡ ፀብዕ፡ መርቆሬዎስ፡ ቀተሎ፡
                    ለኡልያኖስ፡ መምዕላይ። ወሶበ፡ ወግዖ፡ ወድቀ፡ እምላዕለ፡ ፈረሱ፡ ወኡልያኖስ፡ ነሥአ፡ ሐመደ፡ እምድር፡ ወዘረወ፡ ላዕለ፡
                    ወሞተ፡ እኩየ፡ ሞተ። ወጋብኡ፡ ሠራዊቱ፡ ወአንገሡ፡ ህየንቲሁ፡ አኖሬዎስሃ፡ መራቀሬ፡ ሃይማኖተ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወሐነፀ፡ አብያተ፡
                    ክርስቲያናት፡ ወአጽንዖሙ፡ በሀገረ፡ ሮሜ፡ በስመ፡ መርቆሬዎስ፡ ወአስተርአየ፡ ብዙኀ፡ ተአምራት፡  እምይእቲ፡ ቤተ፡
                    ክርስቲያን።</ab>
